Media personality and Loxion Kulca founder Wandile Nzimande, popularly known as DJ 1D, has passed on. Kaya FM reported the sad news on their 6pmbulletin on Wednesday. Following the news of his passing, tributes have been pouring in for the media personality. Podcaster Vivian Machuene said she's heartbroken in her tribute to Wandi. "Never gonna get to see your beautiful smile, hear your infectious laugh, or share in your brilliant ideas again Wandile Nzimande. "I find solace in knowing that you are resting and that every chance I got, I reminded you just how much I love you. Dumedisa Flabba, Jabba le Pro." Many wished for his soul to rest in peace and shared that the streetwear industry has suffered a great loss.